Terrible wings. I love America’s Best but this was by far the worst wings I ever had from any place! I ordered some crab sticks and steak and cheese as well and both were junk. The crab sticks are imitation crab and taste like fried plastic. I ordered everything on the steak and cheese and only got cheese and onions on it. The wings were so soggy and undercooked. The smell made me and two others sick and we barely ate them. I only gave two stars because the customer service was great and the place was clean but don’t let that trick you into not checking your food. Worst America’s Best experience ever.

To be classified as "America's Best Wings" is an exaggeration. Decided to order through UberEats. I order a 5 piece honey mustard combo (all drums). Once my order arrived, I was extremely disappointed! I did not all drums so I was up-charged an extra $1.00 only to receive drums and flats. To add insult to injury, the honey mustard wings were awful. I am certain that they simply pour honey mustard from a container onto the wings. My expectations were obviously way to high because it wasn't marinated into the wings. The wings were hot but the sauce was not. The fries also come unseasoned, which was another letdown. Unfortunately, I would not recommend this place to anyone, especially if you're accustomed to great tasting wings!
